displayProperties.name: Heavy Does It
displayProperties.description:
Complete activities in Vanguard, Gambit, and Crucible playlists; defeat targets using the Grand Overture Exotic Machine Gun. 

Higher tier Nightfall completions, Crucible and Gambit wins, and defeated Guardians provide additional progress.

displayProperties.name: Deepsight Resonance
displayProperties.description:
This weapon possesses a resonance detectable by your Deepsight ability.

Use this weapon in combat or to complete activities in order to attune to this resonance and extract materials useful for shaping weapons.

displayProperties.name: Bring the Overkill
displayProperties.description:
Complete the following objectives in a single run of Dares of Eternity. Objectives will reset if not completed when the activity ends.

Defeat combatants with your Super, disintegrate combatants with high-damage elemental final blows, and complete the activity with an impressive score.

displayProperties.name: Empty Fragment Socket
displayProperties.description:
Fragments are used to modify your abilities. They are shared across subclasses of the same element type.

Currently, you don't have any capacity for fragments. First equip an Aspect to gain energy.

displayProperties.name: Ascendant Alloy
displayProperties.description:
Used in weapon shaping to enhance traits.

Can be obtained from weekly campaign missions in the Throne World and The Witch Queen Offensives. Also can be purchased from the Cryptarch or Banshee-44 in the Tower.

displayProperties.name: Of Queens and Worms
displayProperties.description: Meet with Mara Sov in the Enclave on Mars.

displayProperties.name: Molten
displayProperties.description: Equip this weapon ornament to change the appearance of Dead Messenger. Once you get an ornament, it's unlocked for all characters on your account.

Precision final blows grant a stacking range bonus to this weapon. Non-precision final blows remove range stacks but grant bonus accuracy and stability when all range stacks have been removed.
